<br>
Toris came into the great Palace of Poseidon and Amphitrite, and handed off the scroll to one of the sea Queen's servants.<br>
<br>
Meanwhile, Athena sat smiling in her throne. She took her gaze from the doors of her Temple to Alecto.<br>
<br>
&quot;What should we do when our little guest arrives?&quot; <p>_.- Goddess Athena, Goddess of Wisdom, War, the arts, and crafts -._<br>
